# Home Buddy Pro

## Project Description
Home Buddy Pro is a smart home/property management application developed to help users manage home-related services, bookings, and records efficiently.

## Features
- User-friendly interface
- Manage bookings/details
- Easy navigation
- Organized data management
- Responsive design

## Technologies Used
- TypeScript
- GitHub
- Lovable AI
- Web Technologies

